59\. But when the children among you  
Come of age, let them (also)  
Ask for permission, as do those  
Senior to them (in age):  
Thus does God make clear  
His Signs to you: for God  
Is full of knowledge and wisdom.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/024/024_060.gif)

